message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with medical image analysis using deep learning techniques, which falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper focuses on the segmentation of lumbar vertebrae, which is a medical imaging task (cs.MED). Finally, the use of deep neural networks for this task also falls under the sub-category of neural networks (cs.NEURON).
